        <mxCell id="rules_b" value="✗  Going over 15 minutes&#xa;✗  Status reports instead of board walk&#xa;✗  Problem-solving in the sync&#xa;✗  One person talking &gt;2 min&#xa;✗  Skipping the board, talking abstractly&#xa;✗  Discussing tasks not on the board&#xa;✗  Waiting for absent team members&#xa;&#xa;──────────────&#xa;&#xa;If it takes &gt;15 min → the sync&#xa;is being run incorrectly." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=11;fontColor=#94A3B8;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
